<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>運用実績レポート | CoinPool</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
            background: #0f172a; /* image_0.png準拠の背景色 */
            color: #f1f5f9;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #38bdf8; /* 水色アクセント */
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        /* カード全体のスタイル */
        .card {
            background: #1e293b; /* image_0.png準拠のカード色 */
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #f1f5f9;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        /* 検証条件のグリッド */
        .cond-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .cond-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .cond-label { color: #94a3b8; margin-right: 8px; }
        .cond-value { font-weight: bold; color: #f1f5f9; }

        /* 実績数値とビジュアル */
        .result-layout {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .result-stats { flex: 1; }
        .result-visual { flex: 1; text-align: center; }

        .stat-box { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .stat-label { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #94a3b8; display: block; }
        .stat-value { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: bold; }
        
        .growth-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #fbbf24; /* オレンジイエロー */
            color: #0f172a;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-left: 10px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        /* 簡易グラフ風バー */
        .chart-bar-bg {
            height: 12px;
            background: #0f172a;
            border-radius: 6px;
            position: relative;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .chart-bar-fill {
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 6px;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
        }

        /* 比較セクション */
        .comparison-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .comp-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .vs-circle {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background: #334155;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        /* 結論の強調表示 */
        .conclusion-box {
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #38bdf8;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        /* 外部リンクボタン */
        .btn-link {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #38bdf8;
            color: #0f172a;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-link:hover { background: #7dd3fc; }

        .note { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;}

        /* アイコンの簡易代替 */
        .icon-stub { display: inline-block; width: 1em; text-align: center; color: #38bdf8; margin-right: 5px;}

        @media (max-width: 650px) {
            .result-layout, .comparison-layout { flex-direction: column; grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .vs-circle { margin: 10px auto; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>1年間検証レポート</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Baseチェーン cbBTC/ETH V3 0.3%</p>

    <div class="card">
        <h2><span class="icon-stub">📋</span>検証条件</h2>
        <div class="cond-grid">
            <div class="cond-item"><span class="cond-label">ペア:</span><span class="cond-value">cbBTC / ETH</span></div>
            <div class="cond-item"><span class="cond-label">プール:</span><span class="cond-value">Uniswap V3 0.3%</span></div>
            <div class="cond-item"><span class="cond-label">レンジ:</span><span class="cond-value">±5%</span></div>
            <div class="cond-item"><span class="cond-label">期間:</span><span class="cond-value">365日間</span></div>
            <div class="cond-item"><span class="cond-label">初期資金:</span><span class="cond-value">1,000ドル</span></div>
            <div class="cond-item"><span class="cond-label">リポジション:</span><span class="cond-value">70回/年</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2><span class="icon-stub">📈</span>運用結果（流動性提供）</h2>
        <div class="result-layout">
            <div class="result-stats">
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="stat-label">初期資金</span>
                    <span class="stat-value" style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #94a3b8;">1,000ドル</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="stat-label">累計手数料収益</span>
                    <span class="stat-value" style="color: #10b981;">+3,303.57ドル</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="result-visual">
                <span class="stat-label">最終資産合計</span>
                <span class="stat-value" style="color: #fbbf24;">3,906.06ドル</span>
                <span class="growth-badge">約3.9倍</span>
                <div class="chart-bar-bg">
                    <div class="chart-bar-fill" style="width: 100%; background: #fbbf24;"></div>
                    <div class="chart-bar-fill" style="width: 25%; background: #64748b;"></div> </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; margin-top: 5px;">
                    <span>$1,000</span>
                    <span>$3,906</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2><span class="icon-stub">⚖️</span>パフォーマンス比較</h2>
        <div class="comparison-layout">
            <div class="comp-item">
                <span class="stat-label">単純保有（ガチホ）</span>
                <span class="stat-value" style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 1.4rem;">約670ドル</span>
                <div class="chart-bar-bg" style="margin-top: 15px;">
                    <div class="chart-bar-fill" style="width: 17%; background: #64748b;"></div> </div>
            </div>
            <div class="vs-circle">VS</div>
            <div class="comp-item" style="border: 1px solid #fbbf24;">
                <span class="stat-label" style="color: #fbbf24;">CoinPool型運用</span>
                <span class="stat-value" style="color: #fbbf24; font-size: 1.4rem;">3,906.06ドル</span>
                <div class="chart-bar-bg" style="margin-top: 15px;">
                    <div class="chart-bar-fill" style="width: 100%; background: #fbbf24;"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="conclusion-box">
            資産成長に <span style="font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: bold; color: #fbbf24;">約5.8倍</span> の差がつきました。
        </div>
    </div>

    <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Hgz2ikWBre0xP1paMGIlCdNKl33stJNY/edit?gid=994495645#gid=994495645" class="btn-link" target="_blank">
        実際の検証データをスプレッドシートで見る
    </a>

    <div class="note">
        ※2025/2/6〜2026/2/6（365日）のデータを元にした検証結果です。<br>
        ※レンジ外時は50:50へリポジション。
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
